{{Quote|I can't resist the challenge of rendering strange new worlds and fantastic situations on a daily basis &mdash; filling stark white panels with scenes rich in depth and intensity!|Dave Ross|<ref name="Official site">{{WebCite|url=https://www.daverossart.com/index.html|title=Dave Ross Art|work=Daverossart.com|archivedate=20241009075555}}</ref>}}
'''Dave Ross''' is an artist who has illustrated a number of [[Star Wars comic books|comics]] and comic covers for [[Dark Horse Comics]]. He graduated from the Animation program at [[Wikipedia:Toronto|Toronto's]] [[Wikipedia:Sheridan College|Sheridan College]] and has also worked for both [[Wikipedia:Marvel Comics|Marvel]] and [[Wikipedia:DC Comics|DC]].<ref name="Official site" />

After drawing the covers of [[Legacy (2006) 9|both]] [[Legacy (2006) 10|issues]] of the [[Star Wars: Legacy: Trust Issues|''Trust Issues'']] arc of the ''[[Star Wars: Legacy]]'' comic series in [[2007]], Ross went on to do the interior art for various issues of ''Legacy'', [[Star Wars: Dark Times|''Dark Times'']], and [[Star Wars: The Old Republic (comic series)|''The Old Republic'']].

